            <p class="campaign-kicker">UP College Uniform Protest 2026</p>
            <h1 class="headline">Scholars. Not School children.</h1>
            <p class="hero-subhead">
              Uttar Pradesh's university students are adults, voters, and future professionals.
              A uniform mandate doesn't build discipline — it erases identity, burdens hostel
              students, and distracts from real academic priorities. We are saying no.
            </p>

            <div class="counter-block">
              <p class="counter-label">Current Verified Protests Across UP:</p>
              <p class="counter" id="tally" aria-live="polite">[ 0 ]</p>
              <p class="counter-updated" id="updated">Live count warming up</p>
            </div>

            <a href="#vote-zone" class="hero-cta">Cast Your Vote Now</a>
